Paper: hep-th/9908092

Date: 1999-08-13

Title: Nonpropagation of tachyon on the BTZ black hole in type 0B string theory

Authors: H. W. Lee, Y. S. Myung (Inje University) and Jin Young Kim (Kunsan

University)Comments: some detailed explanations are added, modified version will be

appeared in Physics Letters B, 11 pages in RevTeX, no figuresJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B466 (1999) 211-215

We obtain the BTZ black hole (AdS$_3 \times$S$^3$) as a non-dilatonicsolution from type 0B string theory. Analyzing the perturbation around thisblack hole background, we show that the tachyon is not a propagating mode.